  "text": "without using combinations of specific antibodies. It remains to be seen whether more refined immunological techniques will result in detection of an Alp3-specific antigenic marker. Due to its cross-reactivity with other Alps, Alp3 may be of considerable interest as a vaccine candidate in a CPS/Alp3 conjugate vaccine, as a free protein, or as a recombinant version of antigenic Alp3 domains [CITATION_1] . A summary of immunological characteristics of Alp2 and Alp3 is included in Fig. 3 and Table 1 .",
